python:
sudo apt-get install idle3
python3 -m pip install sounddevice
sudo apt-get install python3-soundfile
sudo apt-get install portaudio19-dev

Arduino:
sudo git clone https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-PWM-Servo-Driver-Library.git
	(/usr/share/arduino/libraries)

Autoexec:
/etc/profile

PulseAudio:
pacmd list-sinks
pacmd set-default-sink [index|name] // Will select audio output automatically after BTConnect if set once?

Bluetooth:
bluetoothctl devices
bluetoothctl paired-devices
bluetoothctl connect [MAC:ADDRESS]
